Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.14,0:21:25.56,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Bleed my heart dry
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.56,0:21:29.56,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Leave me here to die
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.56,0:21:31.65,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}It’ll be all on you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.65,0:21:32.90,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Said, “gimme your heart”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:35.69,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}So I filled it up with all of my love
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:39.07,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Gave it to you, trusted that you would keep it safe
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:42.62,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}It thrived upon your vibe
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.62,0:21:44.78,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Beating in sync with yours at night
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:48.62,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}You poured your soul into mine with just a wink
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.04,0:21:52.46,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}So why don’t you want my heart no more?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.46,0:21:54.84,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}It’s gathering dust on your bedroom floor
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.84,0:21:57.92,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Do what you want, decision’s yours
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:21:59.84,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}I’ll be alright
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:02.59,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}If you won’t take it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:06.56,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}You might as well bleed it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:07.81,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Squeeze it like a lemon
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.81,0:22:09.77,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Like a rag you’ll throw away
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:12.60,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Bleed my heart dry
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:15.90,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Leave me here to die
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.69,0:22:19.74,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}It’ll be all on you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.74,0:22:21.74,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}I know you’ll do what’s right
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.74,0:22:25.66,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}And be right by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.12,0:22:28.45,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Won’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:30.83,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Why won’t, why won’t you bleed my heart dry?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.83,0:22:34.50,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Why don’t you leave me here to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.50,0:22:37.75,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Why won’t you bleed my heart dry?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:39.96,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}You know that I’ll put it all on you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:43.93,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}I trust you’ll know just what to do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.51,0:22:49.14,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}I’ll be right here, forever waiting for you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.14,0:21:25.56,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}榨乾我的心臟
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.56,0:21:29.56,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}留我一人等死
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.56,0:21:31.65,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}全都是因為你
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.65,0:21:32.90,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}你說“給我你的心”
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.90,0:21:35.69,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}於是我用全部的愛將其填滿
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.69,0:21:39.07,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}把它給你  相信你會保管好
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.49,0:21:42.62,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}它在你的薰陶下蓬勃
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.62,0:21:44.78,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}在夜晚與你心跳同步
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.78,0:21:48.62,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}你只用眨眼就讓我魂牽夢繞
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.04,0:21:52.46,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}為什麼你不再想要我的心了？
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.46,0:21:54.84,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}它在你的臥室地板積灰
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.84,0:21:57.92,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}做你想做的  都取決於你
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.92,0:21:59.84,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}我沒事的
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.59,0:22:02.59,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}如果你不接受它
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.59,0:22:06.56,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}或許也會榨乾它
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.56,0:22:07.81,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}像擠壓一個檸檬
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.81,0:22:09.77,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}像一塊無用抹布
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.39,0:22:12.60,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}榨乾我的心臟
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.60,0:22:15.90,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}留我一人等死
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.69,0:22:19.74,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}全都是因為你
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.74,0:22:21.74,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}我知道你會做正確的事
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.74,0:22:25.66,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}陪在我的身邊
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.12,0:22:28.45,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}對嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.45,0:22:30.83,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}為什麼你不榨乾我的心臟？
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.83,0:22:34.50,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}為什麼你不留我一人等死？
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.50,0:22:37.75,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}為什麼你不榨乾我的心臟？
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.75,0:22:39.96,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}你知道我會全部交給你
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.96,0:22:43.93,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}我相信你知道該做什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.51,0:22:49.14,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}我會在這裡  永遠等著你
